wait and see ♪

47:03.792 --> 47:05.208
-Whoa.
-Hey, hey.

47:05.208 --> 47:07.875
Fuck, you know what?
I'm sorry, bro.

47:07.875 --> 47:09.625
-[grunts]
-What the fuck you want, huh?

47:09.625 --> 47:11.000
[glass shatters]

47:12.542 --> 47:14.667
Come on,
you piece of shit!

47:16.667 --> 47:18.041
[yells]

47:18.041 --> 47:19.709
Oh, fuck! What the fuck?

47:19.709 --> 47:21.333
[grunting]

47:25.041 --> 47:26.333
[Hank]
Fuck this.

47:26.333 --> 47:28.000
Decourcy said to wait.

47:29.542 --> 47:31.375
[grunts]

47:31.375 --> 47:33.291
Piece of shit!

47:33.291 --> 47:34.625
Fuck you!

47:38.875 --> 47:40.709
