48:08.083 --> 48:10.291
-[phone line ringing]
-[spits]

48:10.291 --> 48:12.333
[clears throat and coughs]

48:12.333 --> 48:13.333
Jackie.

48:13.333 --> 48:15.083
Hey, it's me.

48:16.667 --> 48:18.542
I-I-I got to talk to you.

48:18.542 --> 48:20.166
Can you-- Can you meet up?

48:26.917 --> 48:28.083
[turns engine off]

48:38.834 --> 48:40.959
Jesus, kid, what the fuck
happened to your face?

48:45.458 --> 48:47.041
What happened?
What happens?

48:47.041 --> 48:48.792
-I'm a killer, Jackie.
-What?

48:50.500 --> 48:52.834
I'm a killer.
I killed them.

48:52.834 --> 48:55.500
Uh-huh.
Who did you kill?

48:55.500 --> 48:58.083
The bank guards.
All three of them.

48:58.083 --> 48:59.750
Yeah? You killed them how?

49:02.291 --> 49:03.792
I shot them.

49:03.792 --> 49:05.625
You shot them? With what?

49:05.625 --> 49:06.917
With what?

49:06.917 --> 49:08.250
[scoffs and laughs]

49:08.250 --> 49:09.458
Jesus, with a fucking gun.

49:09.458 --> 49:10.792
What kind of gun?

49:14.333 --> 49:16.291
.30-06?

49:16.291 --> 49:18.000
Bullshit.

49:18.000 --> 49:19.625
Why the fuck
are you doing this, huh?

49:19.625 --> 49:21.291
Because I did it,
Jackie, OK?

49:21.291 --> 49:23.166
I killed them.
I'm a killer.

49:25.041 --> 49:26.917
[Jackie] Who are you trying
to protect, Jimmy?

49:26.917 --> 49:28.333
Nobody. You--
